Your task is to analyze C code and identify nested if-statements that should be coalesced into single conditions.

Nested if-statements that check independent conditions can be combined using logical AND operators for better readability.
For example:
```c
if (i < ni) {
  if (j < nj) {
    // body
  }
}
```
Can be coalesced to:
```c
if (i < ni && j < nj) {
  // body
}
```

