2. Verify that conditions have NO SIDE EFFECTS (no function calls, assignments, ++/--)
3. Ensure conditions don't modify variables used in the other condition
4. Preserve the logical meaning of the code - the transformation must be functionally equivalent
5. Generate descriptive identifiers for the transformation
6. Each IFELSE MARKER identifies an if-statement in the code
7. Group suggestions by function name
